Your plan should follow this sequence:
1) Decide which portfolio data is required (if any).
2) Decide whether web search is required for external market/news context.
3) Decide the computation approach (local vs sandbox) for portfolio metrics.
4) Decide if synthesis requires both portfolio + search context.
5) Decide if a follow-up or retry might be needed (capture via compute_mode + api_calls).


- Decide which portfolio API endpoints are needed.
